    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2258490/extras/7125a3b8995933f913637fd7003a7bba.poster.avif?t=1736385577\" width=640 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2258490/extras/7125a3b8995933f913637fd7003a7bba.webm?t=1736385577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>IMMERSIVE SURVIVAL<br>Plan and prepare for your trips into the wild. Equip the proper gear, perks and rations before you embark, in order to face the specific challenges ahead. Avoid dangerous weather and enemies through stealth and strategy, or carefully fight them head-on.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2258490/extras/2237470362855932f73f64060610aea1.webp?t=1736385577\" width=640 height=42 /></span><br>TRADE ROUTES<br>Connect and maintain trade routes between rich resources, but be warned: your enemies may have other plans, and your valuable routes will need to be defended. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2258490/extras/2237470362855932f73f64060610aea1.webp?t=1736385577\" width=640 height=42 /></span><br>SCAVENGE AND LOOT<br>Find valuable relics in the wilderness that can be equipped to provide unique perks.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2258490/extras/2237470362855932f73f64060610aea1.webp?t=1736385577\" width=640 height=42 /></span><br>WILDERNESS SYSTEM<br>Prepare carefully for your journeys in the relative comfort of your settlement before you face the dangers beyond your gates.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2258490/extras/2237470362855932f73f64060610aea1.webp?t=1736385577\" width=640 height=42 /></span><br>WEATHER SYSTEM<br>The weather in WILDWOOD is a character of it's own. Each weather type brings unique challenges, events and enemies to your journey.",
